{"tid":1936503,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★醫管局調亂亞博館四個樣本，兩個陽性當作陰性，患者一度獲放行回家。","createTime":"2020-03-21T09:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T09:31:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"73058e3d735ad7cdb55ef224c341e2449ff3b815","tid":1936503,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T09:13:28.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒肺炎（俗稱武漢肺炎）疫情嚴峻，今日增17宗確診20宗初步陽性，3月14日愉景灣婚禮共六人染病；加拿大及玻利維亞團共七人染病。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>醫管局調亂亞博館四個樣本，兩個陽性當作陰性，患者一度獲放行回家。<br />\n</strong><br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥下午6點見記者，據了解，政府將加強機場抵港旅客的病毒測試，除了為已出現病徵的旅客化驗新型冠狀病毒，會擴大至沒有病徵的旅客都會檢測。因應推出新措施，現時亞洲博覽館會的臨時檢疫中心空間將進一步擴展。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/450663/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD-%E5%A2%9E17%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA20%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E9%99%BD%E6%80%A7-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E5%85%AD%E9%BB%9E%E8%A6%8B%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F450663%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2592%25AD-%25E5%25A2%259E17%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA20%25E5%2588%259D%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E9%2599%25BD%25E6%2580%25A7-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5%25E5%2585%25AD%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25A6%258B%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=8244e9bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/450663/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD-%E5%A2%9E17%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA20%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E9%99%BD%E6%80%A7-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E5%85%AD%E9%BB%9E%E8%A6%8B%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85</a>"},{"pid":"b924de36bea470db9826a4d1bf6e495803b3e334","tid":1936503,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T09:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.g